{"tid":858717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落實公務員要受國情教育 觀塘將建公務員學院","createTime":"2018-10-12T04:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T05:10:05.000Z","uid":72963,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53a902e0d7fdcec6f277e17de8f095e1f1dd6361","tid":858717,"uid":72963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:06:05.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局長羅智光今早（10月12日）表示，已敲定在觀塘的官地興建公務員學院，又直言公務員接受國情教育是有實際工作需要。  羅智光闡釋施政報告，指公務員接受國情教育有實際工作需要，部分國家策略可能會影響香港，公務員需要了解中國發展，以茲應對，完全沒有所謂的「洗腦」。  羅智光又指已決定在鄰近觀塘港鐵站的政府用地興建公務員學院。有指該地段地理位置優越，建屋會否更好，羅智光辯解指項目會加入地區康體中心、綠化步道等，是活化觀塘區的大好機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-12-2018/48641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-12-2018%2F48641&d=651rJW1QGseCj5pgdxcXthxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=0585579e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-12-2018/48641</a><br />\n<br />\n洗腦集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca8df855b2adffb9d7b73835b035e03022b0f1d","tid":858717,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"公務員再教育<br />\n入得政府預左啦"},{"pid":"61cc8a6d83fe2bfa4782a3a2a9ec3d0cef40506e","tid":858717,"uid":82974,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"多重國籍，家人子女在西方國家生活嗰班官洗唔洗再教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447cfb4fb28c7f00b975479bead288973140ab46","tid":858717,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"禁公務員子女讀國際學校 到外國讀書"},{"pid":"2233709ed0ad89f9919b7a8f2a8ac79e7911f3ba","tid":858717,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61cc8a6d83fe2bfa4782a3a2a9ec3d0cef40506e","tid":858717,"uid":82974,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"多重國籍，家人子女在西方國家生活嗰班官洗唔洗再教育<img src=